# ============================================================================
# SERVER-SIDE ONLY - DO NOT PREFIX WITH NEXT_PUBLIC_
# ============================================================================

# Yellow Server Private Key (REQUIRED when YELLOW_MOCK_MODE=false)
# This key is used to sign channel operations (create, resize, close)
#
# To generate a new key:
#   cast wallet new
#
# Security requirements:
# 1. Fund this wallet with small ETH for gas on Base Mainnet (~0.01 ETH)
# 2. This wallet will hold platform funds during channel operations
# 3. Never commit this key to version control
# 4. Use environment variables or secrets management in production
#
# YELLOW_SERVER_PRIVATE_KEY=0xac0974bec39a17e36ba4a6b4d238ff944bacb478cbed5efcae784d7bf4f2ff80
